Same problem.<br />
<br />
MgrEditCtl is a user control containing a three column grid, that I would like to expand to the windows columns, but it gets to a fixed size and doesnt stretch when the window is maximized.<br />
<br />
I suppose I could write it as a fixed size, and manually expand it, but as Kill Nine says, its &quot;Super Annoying.&quot;<br />
<pre><code>&lt;mui:ModernWindow.MenuLinkGroups&gt;
